    "long_instructions": "## Brainstorming Initial Ideas Chat\r\n\r\nUse AI Chat to help you come up with early ideas for your product launch. Think creatively about features, branding, and messages that would connect with adults working from home.\r\n\r\nFocus on ideas that connect to your assigned role (e.g., name + slogan, visuals, script, or jingle).\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n1. Use AI Chat to brainstorm creative possibilities for your product or campaign.\r\n    - What could this product include or do to support people working from home?\r\n    - What are some possible names, taglines, looks, sounds, or messages?\r\n    - How might this product solve everyday challenges remote workers face?\r\n    - What images, examples, or documents could you share with AI to inspire fresh ideas?\r\n2. As you brainstorm, start filling in the creative role sections of your group slide deck (logo + slogan, jingle, or script, depending on your role).\r\n3. Want better results? Ask AI to give you options in different styles—for example: professional, playful, minimalist, futuristic, or quirky.",
